2001-05-18 18:33  pgregory

	* libddmsock/win32/intel/ddmsock.cpp, render/renderer.cpp,
	  render/texturemap.cpp, texer/texer.cpp: Chnage to CqFile, the
	  main CqFile now takes an optional searchpath string as a ';'
	  separated list of pathspecs. CqRiFile derives from CqFile and
	  provides the ability to fetch the searchpath from the Ri options.

